      "message": "This name comes from the specification https://www.dmtf.org/sites/default/files/standards/documents/DSP0248_1.3.0.pdf  Table 106 – Redfish Action PDR format - the area with the fields `RelatedResourceCount` and `RelatedResourceID [...]` is marked as `Host Resource Information`\n\nWith that fact in mind, do we still want to change `host-\u003erelated` everywhere?",
