      "side": 1,
      "message": "Given the two `foreach` macros have to be used sequentially after the call to `decode_pldm_platform_redfish_action_pdr()`, perhaps we only provide the complete example code in the documentation for `decode_pldm_platform_redfish_action_pdr()` and just document the parameters for the macros.\n\nMy concern is that both examples are incomplete. The sensible place for a complete examples seems to be `decode_pldm_platform_redfish_action_pdr()`.",
