      "side": 1,
      "message": "I realised I was commenting on the redfish action PDR patch here, where previously I commented on the redfish resource PDR patch.\n\nAnyway, we should probably expand the `pldm_msgbuf_skip()` API to cover `const` buffers.",
      "revId": "a2f9c8ed32403586bfcbe614c52183aef790f585",
