      "writtenOn": "2026-03-12T09:29:09Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Whould there be any difference between the `pldm_msgbuf_skip(ctx, len)` and `pldm_msgbuf_span_required(ctx, len, NULL);` ?\n\nShouldn\u0027t `pldm_msgbuf_skip` call `pldm_msgbuf_span_required(ctx, len, NULL);` inside of it?\n\nOr why do we have a possibility to call `pldm_msgbuf_span_required(ctx, len, NULL);` if we don\u0027t really want to use it.",
